Equation (81) forms a basis for the two-moment model for neutrino transport. Since neutrinos exchange lepton number and four-momentum with the fluid, Eq. (79) needs to be considered, as well. However, these equations are not independent. Due to the relations [obvious from the definitions in Eqs. (74)–(76)]83Nν=-uμεTμνandTνρ=-uμεQμνρ,\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
