				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${\mathbf {S}}_{\text{ avd,e }}$$\end{document}, but the reason for this is not clear.

